---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof for Massage Therapists — Client Testimonials That Build a Full Schedule | SocialProof" description="Massage therapists: automate client testimonials to build trust, reduce no-shows, and fill your schedule. SocialProof makes it easy to collect and display social proof.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Massage Therapists
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        A full massage practice runs on recurring clients and referrals. But those referrals need somewhere to land — a website that instantly communicates your expertise and the experiences real clients have had. SocialProof gives massage therapists a simple way to collect and display those stories.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">New clients need reassurance before they book</h2>
      <p>Getting a massage involves physical vulnerability and a lot of trust. First-time clients are asking: Is this therapist skilled? Are they professional? Will I feel comfortable? When your website shows a dozen genuine client testimonials answering those questions, the decision to book becomes easy.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Without testimonials, a new client has no way to gauge you versus the five other therapists they found in the same search. Price becomes the only differentiator — and you don't want to compete on price.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The testimonials that convert massage clients</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Skill & technique:</strong> "Best deep tissue massage I've had in 10 years. Actually addressed my shoulder issue."</li>
        <li><strong>Atmosphere & comfort:</strong> "The whole experience felt like a spa. I immediately felt at ease."</li>
        <li><strong>Therapeutic results:</strong> "My chronic neck pain is down 70% after a series of sessions."</li>
        <li><strong>Professionalism:</strong> "Always on time, communicative about pressure, and remembered my problem areas from last time."</li>
        <li><strong>Worth-the-price:</strong> "Not the cheapest option — but absolutely worth it. I keep coming back monthly."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for your practice</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Add the widget</strong> to your booking page, about page, or homepage in minutes.</li>
        <li><strong>After a session</strong>, send your SocialProof link via text or email — clients submit feedback in under 2 minutes.</li>
        <li><strong>Review and approve</strong> with one click, and testimonials go live instantly.</li>
        <li><strong>Rotate featured testimonials</strong> by specialty — deep tissue, prenatal, sports massage, etc.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for every massage specialty</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Swedish & relaxation massage</li>
        <li>Deep tissue & sports massage</li>
        <li>Prenatal massage</li>
        <li>Hot stone & specialty treatments</li>
        <li>Medical & therapeutic massage</li>
        <li>Lymphatic drainage</li>
        <li>Corporate chair massage</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background:#fff7ed;border:1px solid #fed7aa;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;color:#9a3412;">
          "I was booked maybe 60% of the time before adding testimonials. Six months later I'm turning people away. The testimonials on my booking page make the difference — people come in already trusting me."
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#7c2d12;">— Licensed massage therapist, solo practice</p>
      </div>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Free forever for solo practitioners</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for 1 active widget — perfect for a solo practice. As you grow to multiple locations or service pages, our paid plans scale with you affordably. No long-term contracts, no setup fees.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <a href="/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#2563eb;color:white;padding:0.85rem 2.2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
          Start free today
        </a>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#888;">Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

